== Installation ==

= Installing the plugin =

1. Unpack the crunchy-sharing.zip.
2. Upload the file to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory.
3. Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress.
4. Configure the options under Admin Panel WP Sharing -> General Options.
5. Activate your license by putting your activation key which you got in your email under Admin Panel WP Sharing -> Activate License.
6. Done and Ready.

